Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.12,0:00:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.21,0:00:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
