Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.57,0:00:59.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,渔夫对于我们的海底朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:00:59.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fishermen have quite an effect
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.28,0:01:00.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有着不小的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:00.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on our undersea friends
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:03.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(411,470)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.29,0:01:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你擦完甲板了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, have you finished swabbing the deck?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.91,0:01:04.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:04.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.58,0:01:06.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九号桌底下有个难搞的藤壶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:06.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a nasty barnacle under table nine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.75,0:01:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're back
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你们说  它们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're back, I tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我亲眼看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw with my own eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hooks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.34,0:01:16.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:16.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hooks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.97,0:01:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能吃个口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a mint?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.47,0:01:19.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:19.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hooks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.64,0:01:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hooks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不可以打包外带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you make that to go?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都不知道自己运气有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't know how lucky you are
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.06,0:01:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hooks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.93,0:01:26.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:26.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So there I was
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干我自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,minding my own business
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.85,0:01:31.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是很想再听你讲精彩的海底故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:31.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love to hear another of your riveting sea tales
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but, um
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.03,0:01:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去检查我垃圾桶了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to do my wastebasket inspections
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.49,0:01:36.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  里面有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:36.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, there's one
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.74,0:01:37.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:37.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别说我没警告过你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't say I didn't warn you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警告他什么  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Warn him about what, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是钩子  我的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hooks, me bucko
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.79,0:01:45.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:45.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're back
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beware the hooks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.17,0:01:48.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:48.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hooks?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, the hooks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.71,0:01:51.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们会垂下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They dangle down
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.79,0:01:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用愉悦的形状和诱人的颜色勾引你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and draw you close with their pleasing shapes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and their beguiling colors
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.97,0:01:59.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到你自以为找到了一片乐土
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And just when you think
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you found the land of milk and honey
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们就会就会扒你裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they grab you by the britches
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高高地把你拉上天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and haul you way up high
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后再高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then higher
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and higher
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and higher
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直到把你拉到海面之上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until you're hauled up to the surface
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.48,0:02:09.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四处扑腾  大口喘气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:09.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,flopping and gasping for breath
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.98,0:02:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后那些东西就会把你做成吃的吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then they cook you and then they eat you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者更惨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or worse
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还会有什么东西比那更惨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What could be worse than that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼品店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gift shops
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(623,236)}礼品店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:19.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(721,214)}海星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:19.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1191,284)}各色贝壳
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要让它抓到我  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let it get me, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.16,0:02:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们不会抓到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they won't get you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.16,0:02:28.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好听蟹老板的话就不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:28.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not as long as you listen to old Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回厨房去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get back to the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.21,0:02:29.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间就是金钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:29.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time is money
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.79,0:02:31.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:31.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  蟹堡王的员工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Krusty crew
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猜怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘉年华来城里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The carnival's in town
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快一起过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还不能走  我在上班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't leave now, I'm working
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.47,0:02:47.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不算走  你那算休息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:47.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not leaving, you're just taking a break
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要去嘉年华  要去嘉年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to the carnival, going to the carniv
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.69,0:02:59.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要去嘉年华  要去嘉年华
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:59.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to the carnival, going to the carnival
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘉年华回城里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The carnival is back in town
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要排第一个  把所有项目都玩一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be first in line for everything
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.12,0:03:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早些时候有个小朋友来过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There was one kid here earlier
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,样子感觉不像我玩过的嘉年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like any carnival I ever
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.51,0:03:20.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别去  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:20.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别去摸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.47,0:03:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是嘉年华  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't the carnival, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those are hooks
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板说钩子特别危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs says they're really dangerous
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没感觉到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sense no danger here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些东西怎么会危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could they be dangerous?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面还放着白送的奶酪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're covered with free cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只知道蟹老板说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I know is, Mr. Krabs said
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.07,0:03:38.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:38.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别那样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheesy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No danger here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on, try it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可蟹老板说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Krabs said
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我来问问你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, let me ask you something
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.91,0:03:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这看起来危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does this look dangerous?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.96,0:03:56.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:56.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能放松点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lighten up, will you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.30,0:04:03.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是说得要我自个把奶酪全吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:03.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or do I have to eat all this cheese by mysel
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, come back
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're alive
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I ever
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should try it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是怎么对付海平面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about the surface
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有裤子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and your britches
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.57,0:04:24.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有礼品店的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:24.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the gift shops?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.95,0:04:28.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁升得还不算高赶紧跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:28.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just jump off before you go up too high
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板交代过我不该靠近那些东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs said I shouldn't get near those things
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那他说过你不应该爬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did he say you shouldn't climb on top of them
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后当马骑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and ride them like a horsy?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, no
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计是没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess he didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,衣鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silverfish
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Away
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杰罗尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Geronimo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.15,注释,,0,0,0,,[ Geronimo：感叹词，尤在从高空跳下时喊出 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.69,0:05:07.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比在蟹堡王加班好玩多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is more fun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:07.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than double overtime at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(411,500)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,P.U.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你管这叫吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You call this food?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我三明治味道像炸靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My sandwich tastes like a fried boot
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我三明治就是个炸靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My sandwich is a fried boot
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能做快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up, will you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都饿坏了  看看大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're hungry over here, look at us
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我孩子啥都吃不到  让我都快没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My kids haven't eaten and I'll die
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这么翻肉饼不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not how you're supposed to flip it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.22,0:05:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们干什么非得吃这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to eat this stuff anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the halibut's going on in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家争着想要吃的  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a feeding frenzy, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且海绵宝宝还没休息完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and SpongeBob's not back from his break
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为你说海绵宝宝在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you said SpongeBob was taking a break
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自从59年的海霸大饥荒以来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's taken a break at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人都不让休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,since the chum famine of '59
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚说什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what were you saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He took
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a break
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.38,0:06:06.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  懒鬼宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:06.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, SpongeBob lazypants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll find you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.59,0:06:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这鼻子能闻到一万里格远的懒鬼味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This nose can smell laziness for up to 10,000 leagues
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要给你好好休息一场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a break
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.81,0:06:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好让你永生难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll not soon forget
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.73,0:06:20.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板  我需要人帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:20.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Krabs, I still need help
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They should be right here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Again
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hooks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一  二  三
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two, three
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boys
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是慢了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wasn't quick enough
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们就这么没了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're gone
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.18,0:06:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我能再把他抱进怀里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I could only hold him in me arms again
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  我就
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, I'd
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就狠狠把他们掐住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd throttle them
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是怎么跟你交代钩子的事的  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you about those hooks, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.56,0:07:00.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:00.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.19,0:07:00.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:00.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来跟你们说说钩子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about the hooks
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.31,0:07:05.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要骑上钩子升升升
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:05.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ride them up and up and up
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后慢慢地飘下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then you gently float down
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.57,0:07:12.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知不知道飘不回来会出什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And do you know what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you don't float back down?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼品店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gift shop?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更惨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Worse
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.37,0:07:18.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到头来你们会被真空包装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:18.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You end up vacuum-packed
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,塞进金枪鱼罐头里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a can of tuna
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717,750)}金枪鱼
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,日子完全没盼头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With nothing to look forward to
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能闻蛋黄酱的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but the smell of mayonnaise
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(753,798)}蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几个小子得向我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you boys to promise me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不去骑那些钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll never go on those hooks again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们保证  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We promise, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要的是水手宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a sailor's promise
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟着我做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Repeat after me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会再靠近钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Near the hooks I'll never go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不会再靠近钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Near the hooks we'll never go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.57,0:07:48.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍的妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:48.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother of pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甲板起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire on the poop deck
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.74,0:07:52.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍的妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:52.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother of pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甲板起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire on the poop deck
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.41,0:07:54.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:54.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, then
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶快离开这个死亡陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of this deathtrap anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是全新的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,today is a new day
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好向蟹老板证明自己很忠诚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to prove myself loyal to Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.21,0:08:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你走错路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going the wrong way
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上班向来都走这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always go to work this way
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天不用上班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not going to work today
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to go play
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hooky
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是派大星  我们宣过誓的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Patrick, we promised
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我手指交叉  运气可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had my fingers crossed
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你根本就没手指  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have fingers, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个蟹老板就是个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that Mr. Krabs is just a big dummy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱都玩钩子玩一整天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We played on those hooks all day long
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也没出过什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and nothing happened to us
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可蟹老板说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Krabs said
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是要听大笨蛋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you going to listen to a big dummy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是要听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or are you going to listen to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会见  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去痛快玩耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go have some fun
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知道你很想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know you want to
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道我很想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know I want to
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我跟蟹老板宣过誓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I promised Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会再去靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go near another
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hook
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.82,0:09:16.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:16.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板跟我说过你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs told me all about you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是个大骗子  谎话精
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are a liar, a deceiver
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会再中你的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never fall for your tricks again
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个位子有人坐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this seat taken?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴摆脱了想玩钩子的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad I got that out of my system
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.05,0:09:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hooked
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.51,0:09:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that means
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(543,880)}金枪鱼
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被钩住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hooked
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, help
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.19,0:09:49.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:49.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It happened
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.90,0:09:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被钩住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hooked
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.82,0:09:51.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:51.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the hook
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the hook
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.11,0:09:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼品店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gift shop
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.90,0:09:54.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,金枪鱼罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:54.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tuna can
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mayonnaise
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你朋友喝的免费白水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free water for all your little friends
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, dad
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.25,0:10:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了给蟹老板留个小费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just don't forget to leave a tip for old Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.79,0:10:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都迟到两分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're two minutes late
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干什么迟到了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kept you, laddie?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知道我们昨天谈到过的钩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know those hooks we were talking about yesterday?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.88,0:10:20.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没告诉过你不要靠近钩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:20.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you not to go near those hooks?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.14,0:10:21.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:21.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说有  有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean yes, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你告诉过我不要靠近钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you told me not to go near them
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没坐钩子上玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you weren't playing on those hooks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,were you, laddie?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  算是没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, not exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  我坐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我坐上去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I admit it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我好羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I'm so ashamed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  看看我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, look at me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被钩住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hooked
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钩得还挺深
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's in there pretty deep
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.71,0:10:51.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:51.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有一个办法了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing to do, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能脱裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take off my pants
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不能面对着这群
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not in front of all these
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.10,0:11:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,girls
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.14,0:11:09.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我这就脱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:09.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm taking them off
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.98,0:11:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就脱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm taking them off
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.02,0:11:13.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:13.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lad
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.49,0:11:19.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:19.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.11,0:11:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I can't do it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种事绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything but that
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I understand
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是个不错的煎炸厨师  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were a good little fry cook, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(653,262)}招聘
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过咱会另外招人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we'll find another
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿能招到能听蟹老板话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hopefully, one that will listen to old Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我会听话的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I'll listen
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你救救我  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please save me, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证我会表现好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll be good
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是光身子宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's SpongeBob nudiepants
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.78,0:12:06.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝这种模样我可太想看了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:06.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that was more of SpongeBob than I needed to see
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.08,0:12:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生  你钓鱼技术实在是高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward, that was some fine angling
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得那小子学到教训了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think the lad has learned his lesson?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想他会记得非常久的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think he'll remember this for a long time
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pants
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.04,0:12:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我肯定会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know I will
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.88,0:12:17.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:17.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The underwear
