Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by the power of Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有他的年轻小跟班相助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aided by his young ward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有他的年轻小跟班相助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,aided by his young ward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.31,0:13:20.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用敏捷又强大的技艺保护海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:20.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Protecting the sea with feats of strength and agility
