Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:52.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are you ready to hear the winner of this week's contest?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,优胜者将会赢得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our winner will receive
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一样特别机密珍藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a special secret collector's item
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出自美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the adventures of Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,优胜者是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the winner is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黑面宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Springboob Squirepin
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特地做美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I worked forever
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on those life-size Krabby Patty mannequins
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等身蟹黄堡模型做了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他制作了美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for these life-size Krabby Patty mannequins
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等身蟹黄堡模型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黑面宝宝盗了我的创意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Springboob Squirepin stole my idea
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.09,0:14:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.46,0:14:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来刚刚不小心念错名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It appears I've made a slight error in pronunciation
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,优胜者的真正大名是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The real name of the winner is
