Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my prize
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海螺号角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The conch signal
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出自美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From the adventures of Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟电视上的一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As seen on TV
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想知道还能不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it still works?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1079,662)}荫凉滩疗养院
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海螺号角
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The conch signal
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往无影船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the invisible boatmobile
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Barnacleboy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.65,0:15:32.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是不是还没上无影船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:32.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not in the invisible boatmobile, are we?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早跟你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把船做成无影这种事特别傻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,making the boatmobile invisible was a stupid idea
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.95,0:15:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出来  快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come out, come out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wherever you are
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's got to be here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.42,0:15:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士  我好像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mermaidman, I think I
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Found it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点上车  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, get a move on, son
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.17,0:15:51.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们时间不多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:51.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't have all day
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ignition on
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Throttle up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能海螺号角用不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe the conch signal doesn't work anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,激活鱼雷模式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Activate torpedo mode
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.66,0:16:15.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有七鹅男
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:15.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And bobicle bob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩来咱家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman and Barnacleboy in our home
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他已经毁容得不成样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's been horribly disfigured
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blast us
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're too late
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, please
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他没毁容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not disfigured
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就  就
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's, he's
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是那个海绵小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just that sponge kid again
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴再见到你  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good to see you, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,企鹅男孩  我们一定要找出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, Barnacleboy, we've got to find out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海螺号角的声音是哪发出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where that conch signal came from
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我发的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海螺号角就是我吹的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I blew the conch signal, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪里有危险  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the danger, son?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it on
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it on
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.99,0:16:53.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:53.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no danger
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.74,0:16:55.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:55.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No danger?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  一定得有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, there has to be danger
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都吹了海螺号角
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You blew the conch signal
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吹的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and when you blow
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.58,0:17:02.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底是怎么弄到那东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:02.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did you get that thing anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我参加大赛赢来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won it in a contest
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Contest?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,节目组什么事都没跟咱说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't tell us anything anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Spongy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that ain't no toy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.80,0:17:10.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:10.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海螺号角可是个重责大任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The conch signal is an awesome responsibility
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每当它响起  我们都会挺身出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're duty-bound to help whenever it sounds
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是你只能遇到麻烦了再吹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you only blow it when there's trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.93,0:17:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,否则就会出现麻烦  明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or there will be trouble, you got that?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白  先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sirs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good boy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天疗养院卖肉糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're serving meat loaf today
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, goody
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.86,0:17:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝不会随便出什么事就吹海螺号角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't be hearing from me for just anything
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.20,0:17:37.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只会在重大紧急情况才吹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:37.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only for the big emergencies
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能洗快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you hurry up in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺便给我省点热水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And save me some hot water
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海螺号角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The conch signal
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来  年轻小跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come, young ward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.93,0:18:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Youth
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还朝气蓬勃的  就这么没了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cut down in its prime
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说句话  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speak to me, son
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.19,0:18:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open mayonnaise
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:14.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(945,772)}蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只穿着内裤来这
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I come down here in my underwear
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是来开蛋黄酱罐子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to open a jar of mayonnaise?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.70,0:18:19.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:19.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不能到处走  跟别人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't go around socializing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们必须准备好应对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to be prepared for, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,emergencies
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,企鹅男孩  你想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacleboy, think about it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.25,0:18:30.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧急情况现在也不是很经常出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Emergencies don't come around as often as they used to
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以偶尔吹一次海螺号角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can blow the conch every once in a while
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.76,0:18:38.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我们来就给咱事情做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:38.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just give us something to do when we show up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Danger
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我们都累垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're running us ragged
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要响应号角的号召
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,must answer the clarion call
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're exhausted
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.58,0:19:08.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:08.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是有意的  我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it, I
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是想陪着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just wanted to spend time with you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是我的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're my heroes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.34,0:19:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说这些都太晚了  大赛优胜者先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too late for that, Mr. Contest winner
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要毁掉这个东西  用我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to destroy this thing with my
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,硫光眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sulfur vision
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  毁掉它的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll destroy it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是等到回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I get back to the, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼基地再说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mermalair
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至于你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And as for you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.69,0:19:36.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:36.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.98,0:19:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要打击他的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't squash his enthusiasm
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.24,0:19:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟  他可能会当上明天的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After all, he could be the hero of tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.82,0:19:44.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也可能会当上坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:44.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or the villain
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还记得还有个年轻狂小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember another young whippersnapper
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想当个超级英雄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who wanted to be a super-hero
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.12,0:19:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你连吃早饭都不记得  老东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't even remember breakfast, you old coot
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.67,0:20:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能海螺号角蕴含着的责任太重大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe the conch signal is too much responsibility
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.63,0:20:03.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你想不想下午后面的时间一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how would you like to spend
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the rest of the afternoon
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on patrol?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往无影船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the invisible boatmobile
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叮叮当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jingle bells
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士臭  企鹅男孩下了蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman smells, Barnacleboy laid an egg
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:15.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(865,894)}行
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无影船少了个轮胎  而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The invisible boatmobile lost a wheel and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(865,894)}停
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.07,0:20:18.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:18.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I drive?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.73,0:20:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drive?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知道要怎么开无影船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:20.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you know about
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,driving the invisible boatmobile?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.61,0:20:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tons
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如说雨刮器在这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like the windshield wipers are right here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.82,0:20:25.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要碰那个按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:25.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't touch that button
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,折纸按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,origami button
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在城市里巡逻的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When you're patrolling the city
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要谨慎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you always have to be vigilant
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.25,0:20:39.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时时刻刻保持警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:39.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On your toes, constantly alert
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确保有备无患
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always expect the unexpected
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我买到甜甜圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got the donuts
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,企鹅男孩下了蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Barnacle Boy laid an egg
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边那位以前是原子比目鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That fellow over there used to be the atomic flounder
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道他看着不太像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know he doesn't look like much
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是他很有可能会回归犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but he could go back to crime
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猝不及防
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.78,0:21:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.82,0:21:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:08.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(297,346)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, somebody there
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被捕了  原子比目鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest, atomic flounder
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.79,0:21:10.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:10.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let him go
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.83,0:21:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说他可能会失控
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said he could snap
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.04,0:21:12.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猝不及防
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:12.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.16,0:21:13.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:13.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off of me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不是我退休了  我早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I weren't retired, I
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早就
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.01,0:21:24.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:24.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.26,0:21:27.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快滚开  混账
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:27.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of my way, punk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:31.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(841,594)}小餐馆
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我坐着无影船兜风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I rode in the invisible boatmobile
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.60,0:21:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碰到了个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,met a villain
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还学会处理三度烧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and learned to treat third-degree burns
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一天就办这么多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all in one day
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们明天要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So what are we gonna do tomorrow?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.73,0:21:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要不然拿着这一毛钱去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why don't you take this nickel and go over there
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.94,0:21:44.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看点唱机上面有没有我们的主题曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:44.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and see if our theme song is on the jukebox?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.11,0:21:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要知道  他作为一个讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, for a pain in the neck
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是个很棒的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's a pretty nice kid
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快甩了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's ditch him
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.70,0:21:53.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先走  我殿后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:53.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right behind you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点唱机好像没主题曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem to be here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's there, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.75,0:21:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续找
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep looking
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.92,0:22:01.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加把劲  加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:01.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Diligence, diligence
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.55,0:22:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dagnabbit
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.51,0:22:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们刚把无影船停哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did we park the invisible boatmobile?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都找第15遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the 15th time I've looked
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.93,0:22:17.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我绝不能让我英雄们失望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:17.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I can't let my heroes down
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无影船
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boatmobile?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.23,0:22:21.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:21.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.98,0:22:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,企鹅男孩  我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacleboy, I found it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.24,0:22:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尾气管又把你烧伤了是吗  企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still getting burned
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on that tailpipe, huh, Barnacleboy?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.78,0:22:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是肮脏泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the dirty bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.49,0:22:37.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又脏又圆地冒出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:37.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In all his dirty roundness
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.04,0:22:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.50,0:22:42.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是特别舞曲混音版
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:42.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's the special dance mix
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.21,0:22:45.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:45.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.92,0:22:49.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的蟹黄堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:49.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.76,0:22:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩的死对头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.76,0:22:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman and Barnacleboy's archnemesis
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.22,0:22:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The dirty bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.01,0:22:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.77,0:22:59.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你绝对救不回他们  神秘海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:59.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You cannot save them, sponge of mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.44,0:23:02.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们被我超强的表面张力困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:02.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They are trapped by my awesome surface tension
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.52,0:23:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.82,0:23:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是我最爱的超级坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're my most favorite supervillain
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.65,0:23:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我签个名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have your autograph?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.82,0:23:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.49,0:23:10.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:10.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you fool
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.78,0:23:11.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:11.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay back
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.49,0:23:12.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笔尖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:12.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The point
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.49,0:23:15.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心笔尖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.49,0:23:15.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch the point
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.79,0:23:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你救了我们  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.79,0:23:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You saved us, son
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.50,0:23:20.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  你是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:20.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.21,0:23:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是个英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're a hero
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.42,0:23:22.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:22.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.50,0:23:27.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要再来坐着无影船兜风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:24.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you up for another ride
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:27.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the invisible boatmobile?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叮叮当  美人鱼战士臭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jingle bells, Mermaidman smells
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,企鹅男孩下了蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacleboy laid an egg
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡被扎破
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The dirty bubble popped
Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.26,0:23:36.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:36.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.56,0:23:39.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有海绵宝宝逃出生天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:39.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and SpongeBob got away
Dialogue: 1,0:23:41.19,0:23:42.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:42.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch out
